title: Cloud District - Almanacs (2014)
description:
Cloud District - Almanacs (2014)

Debut album from Cloud District. Indie Rock band from Orange County, New York. 

For fans of Modern Baseball, Manchester Orchestra, Brand New, Bad Books, Weezer, The Front Bottoms.

2. Solstice

6. Please Consider Using this song in your Indie Movie
7. Driveways
8. The Guy From The World is a Beautiful Place and I Am No Longer Afraid To Die Added Me On Snapchat
